FBIS3-5030 "dreas042_n_94009" FBIS-EAS-94-042 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Mar 1994 Vietnam Mongolian President Arrives BK0303121594 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 3 Mar 94 BK0303121594 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Mongolian president Punsalmaagiyn Ochirbat arrived in Hanoi Thursday, 3 February, at the invitation of President Le Duc Anh. President Ochirbat was welcomed with red carpet treatment at the Ba Dinh Square in Hanoi. Present at the ceremony, among the others, were President Le Duc Anh and Foreign Minister Nguyen Manh Cam. The two presidents then inspected the guards of honor of the Vietnamese Army. Afterward, the two presidents held cordial meeting at which the Mongolian guest wished that the visit would help him further understand and learn about Vietnam's experiences in its renovation process.
